To start the web server:

1) Open up a shell prompt
2) Navigate to directory containing webserver.lua
3) Run "webs" script


Make sure that the Lua intepreter is in your PATH
or you will have to type the full path to the Lua interpeter
e.g. /path/to/lua webserver.lua

The server runs on port 8080 and can be accessed in 
a web browser with http://localhost:8080

HTML files served by the server should be placed in /www
